	<text xml:lang="">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<lb xml:id="p1z1"/>1544.
					<lb xml:id="p1z2"/>Gratia filii dei tecum. Anna haec Vogleri
					<lb xml:id="p1z3"/>filia iamdudum pluribus exercita sunt, nosti
					<lb xml:id="p1z4"/>mi Bullingere, in Christo observande) adversarii
					<lb xml:id="p1z5"/>institatibus, ne dicam exiliis ab obitu parentis
					<lb xml:id="p1z6"/>non semel ab hero Rapolsteinensi rescire
					<lb xml:id="p1z7"/>voluit debita, qu&#281; pater in profectura zel
					<lb xml:id="p1z8"/>Wirtenbergensi in suum verterit commodum, atque
					<lb xml:id="p1z9"/>ut ratione subducta ex hereditate quod
					<lb xml:id="p1z10"/>superest esset, a solvendo; nam reliqua illi iure
					<lb xml:id="p1z11"/>hereditario debentur. Atqui hactenus, ne gratia
					<lb xml:id="p1z12"/>intelligere, quam vis sedulo viserit, potuit.
					<lb xml:id="p1z13"/>Hinc ad vestros consultandi ergo rediri
					<lb xml:id="p1z14"/>cogitur. Videtur mihi negotium, quantum ego in
					<lb xml:id="p1z15"/>intelligo, esse labefrinthum, ineptricabilem. Admodum
					<lb xml:id="p1z16"/>plurima clam inter herum et Voglerum
					<lb xml:id="p1z17"/>acta sunt, discaphanturum plurimi, ut valde
					<lb xml:id="p1z18"/>ut
					<lb xml:id="p1z19"/>metuo, interfieri solet, in aulis, huius dissidii et
					<lb xml:id="p1z20"/>querulorum sint occasio etc. Est tamen, qui
					<lb xml:id="p1z21"/>plures et alia in suo iuditio ex professo
					<lb xml:id="p1z22"/>mundo manifestabit. De meo statu paucis
					<lb xml:id="p1z23"/>Hoc accipe per aliquot mensis alicumbius, ut
					<lb xml:id="p1z24"/>solenti senes, classicus factus sum, adeo ut ab
					<lb xml:id="p1z25"/>mitumni, nemini vel tota scripserim.
					<lb xml:id="p1z26"/>Mein lieber her und bru&#870;der in Christo
					<lb xml:id="p1z27"/>wellet zu&#870; fur mich bitten, da&#223; mich got
					<lb xml:id="p1z28"/>so es sein wil ist, au&#223; diser zerbrochnen
					<lb xml:id="p1z29"/>h&#252;tti bald auffu&#868;re neuwei&#223;, ich nit dan, da&#223;
					<lb xml:id="p1z30"/>gottes und Christi Iesu evangelium, in hoh von
					<lb xml:id="p1z31"/>achtig ist, und alle laster uber handt, wennen
					<lb xml:id="p1z32"/>Gott helff seinem glaubenbigen, 8. decembris 68.
					<lb xml:id="p1z33"/>Matthic Erb.
					<pb/>
					<lb xml:id="p2z1"/>S.
					<lb xml:id="p2z2"/>B&#252;ro, domino et Henrycho
					<lb xml:id="p2z3"/>viro d. Henrycho
					<lb xml:id="p2z4"/>Bullingero, ecclesi&#281;
					<lb xml:id="p2z5"/>Zurin&#281; antistiti et
					<lb xml:id="p2z6"/>olgo syncere, suo d.
					<lb xml:id="p2z7"/>observando,
				</p>
			</div>
		</body>
	</text>
